        "description": "Beam diameter for precise industrial cleaning; 200 μm recommended for MDF to balance resolution on fibrous surface and large-area coverage, avoiding excessive heat concentration. Finer for details (<150 μm), larger for broad prep (300-500 μm). Source: Equipment specs from Coherent and Trumpf lasers."
